{
  "page": "Loon",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the derogative nickname, see <a href=\"/index.php/Matthar\" title=\"Matthar\">Matthar</a>.</div>\n<p>The <b>Loon</b> inn is one of three inns in the market town of <a href=\"/index.php/Weeping_Town\" title=\"Weeping Town\">Weeping Town</a> which lies on the southern shore of <a href=\"/index.php/Cape_Wrath\" title=\"Cape Wrath\">Cape Wrath</a>. It has a common room. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Loon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Loon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>After Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a> and her party disembark from the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Peregrine\" title=\"Peregrine\">Peregrine</a></i> at Weeping Town Arianne sends <a href=\"/index.php/Joss_Hood\" title=\"Joss Hood\">Joss Hood</a> to the Loon in order to gather intelligence, as she knows the common room is rife with rumors. \n</p><p>In the Loon, Joss learns that half a hundred men and boys from the Weeping Town have set off north to join <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Griffin%27s_Roost\" title=\"Griffin&#39;s Roost\">Griffin's Roost</a>, including young Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Addam_Whitehead\" title=\"Addam Whitehead\">Addam Whitehead</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Old_Lord_Whitehead&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Old Lord Whitehead (page does not exist)\">old Lord Whitehead</a>’s son and heir.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ar2_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ar2-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>That night, Arianne dispatches the first of her <a href=\"/index.php/Raven\" title=\"Raven\">ravens</a> back to <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>, reporting to <a href=\"/index.php/Doran_Martell\" title=\"Doran Martell\">her father</a> on all they'd seen and heard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ar2_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ar2-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Loon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ar2-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ar2_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ar2_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_II_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Arianne II (The Winds of Winter)\">Arianne II (The Winds of Winter)</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404080253\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.021 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.044 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 94/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 522/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 2240/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 471/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 6/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 474/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.52 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   34.627      1 -total\n 84.84%   29.379      1 Template:For\n  6.68%    2.314      1 Template:Warning/twow\n  4.53%    1.568      1 Template:Warning\n  4.31%    1.494      1 Template:References\n  3.04%    1.054      1 Template:Mbox\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:22276-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404080253 and revision id 287841\n -->\n",
